<title>mạ ạ̉ḥsn ạlạ̹kẖwẗa ạ̹dẖ yjtmʿwn bạlwadạd̊</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- mạ ạ̉ḥsn ạlạ̹kẖwẗa ạ̹dẖ yjtmʿwn bạlwadạd̊
 ạ̉krim̊ bạ̉wqạtiⁿ lhm̊ yqḍwnhạ bạlạtḥạd̊

[V2]
 2- bḥbhm jmhwruhm̊ lh slạmu whanạ
 yumtẖĩlwna ạ̉bdạaⁿ ạủlfẗa skạn ạlsmạ

[V3]
 3- bhạʾu wjh rbnạ ynyr dẖạ ạljmʿa ạlmjyd̊
 fturbṭu ạlqlwb bạl ạ̹ymạn wạlrjạ wạlwṭyd̊

[V4]
 4- lnạ yswʿu rạ̉snuạ wnḥn ạ̉ʿḍạʾu ạljsd̊
 flạ sẖiqạquⁿ bynnạ wlạ kẖṣạmuⁿ wḥsd̊

[V5]
 5- ạ̹lhnạ mḥbẗuⁿ whw ạlḥbyb dẖw ạljlạl̊
 wman rʿy̱ ʿhwdhu yrqy ạ̹ly̱ ạ̉wj ạlkmạl̊</lyrics>
</song>